This paper discusses privacy policies and the disclosure of tracking methods, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also involves considerations of privacy and user experience, which could fall under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and information retrieval (cs.PR).
